{"title":"超简单！IOS，在App中使用Safari打开网页（swift）","date":"2019-05-28T16:23:23.000Z","author":"James🐒","link":"post/ios-safariview","tags":["Native"],"categories":["IOS"],"updated":"2019-07-09T14:14:03.412Z","content":"<p>不想用webview？直接使用safari在app中打开网页，而且超级简单，只需两步。</p>\n<p>不说废话，直接开始，简单粗暴</p>\n<h3 id=\"第一步-引入Safari服务\">第一步 引入Safari服务<a href=\"post/ios-safariview#第一步-引入Safari服务\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">import SafariServices</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"第二步-在viewcontroller里实现触发事件\">第二步 在viewcontroller里实现触发事件<a href=\"post/ios-safariview#第二步-在viewcontroller里实现触发事件\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">func showSafariVC(for url: String)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tguard let url = URL(string: url) else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t    return</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tlet safariVC = SFSafariViewController(url: url)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tself.present(safariVC, animated: true, completion: nil)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>就是如此简单！！</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Flutter页面跳转到IOS原生界面   如何实现？","link":"post/flutter-ios-conmmunicate"},"next":{"title":"简单！轻松使用react-navigation","link":"post/rn-reactnavigation"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/ios-safariview/"}